reviewText: I have seen great improvements for years on this program. These are basic, but pertinent strokes, focal points. A master is a master of basics. One can change and modify your styles of course on your own.

I purchased this 2 years ago and returned it.
This style pre-dates the dinosaur.
No one plays tennis like that anymore.
Besides, this was made in the 70's or early 80's and look absolutely horrible on an HD set.
Desperately needs updating.
